Deal +75% Damage with Whips, Claws, and Daggers.
No Affinity Speed decrease while wielding Whips.

She did what?

^orange;You heard me the first time.^reset;

Yea, but we're talking nearly 1000 enemy soldiers. With high-tech armor. And, you know... deadly weapons and what not.

^orange;Right. Well: they're gone now.^reset;

Ok, but is she alright?

^orange;Funny you should ask.^reset;

Uh-oh.

^orange;No, you misunderstand...
She's never been better.

Sudden pressure bending metal -
Forcing bothered dust to settle.
^red;Shhh: do you hear that?^reset;

Fervid death erupts from ashes,
Stealing thought and tearing gashes.
^blue;Shhhh: do you hear that?^reset;

Spreading out and creeping in:
A sentient husk entrenched in sin.
^red;Shhhhh: do you hear that?^reset;

Runes engrave in ruined flesh;
Whispers clash: a garbled mesh.
^blue;Shhhhhh: do you hear that?^reset;

Well...
